                    <p>Bangladesh green environment initiative is a nonprofit youth organization that deals to empowers groups through mentorship and social innovation to become changemakers, engaging them in active citizenship  </p>
                    <p>The organization’s mission is to provide the youth from all socio-economic backgrounds with a platform to make their voice heard and help fulfill their vision for a better world. In Bangladesh, where over 70% of the population is below 40, such a platform is vital to motivate and empower the next generation of leaders to become active citizens and community change makers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Story behind
                        <strong>GoGreenIn</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                    <p>At present environment has become a alarming issue for human living where people are not that much aware about it. They don’t even know how they are affecting the environment. Due to lake to rules & regulation the toxic gas emission rate is increasing day by day which can be result a destructive face for near future.</p>
                    <p>Ground water is the main resource of drinking and other work purpose. Within Dhaka city WASA is supplies more than 80% ground water & 20% surface water instead of having rich portion of surface water resource but people are not aware about how to handle all those resources & how to keep them safe.</p>
                    <p>Unbalanced waste disposal on water body spoil the quality of surface water & most important thing is people don’t even know about it. </p>
                    <p>The main target of BGEI is to reduce problems in Bangladesh regarding hygiene, sanitation, clean water problem, and also present situation of our environment which is getting worse day by day. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">What We Do
                        <strong></strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr><p>
                    • Sanitation: present situation regarding sanitation in urban, undeveloped are like slum or other low living area. At present time they are not aware about hygienic sanitation. So we are helping people to live life in a hygienic way by providing facilities.<br>

• Education: provide facilities to slum people to get minimum educational knowledge<br>
• Health: people are not conscious about their health & other hygiene <br>
• Safe & clean water: having a lot of sources of clean water still people are having toxic substance contaminated water like arsenic .our work is to make people aware about it <br>
• Environmental issues: environment is now a alarming issue. Through providing facilities & training we make people aware about all those issues to reduce all those problem as far as human can avoid <br>
• Waste management: introducing waste separation method, handling, collection, transfer, disposal method to reduce contamination problem.<br>
• Disaster management: since Bangladesh is a disaster prone area. every year people are facing all flood and other problems which causes lots of losses. So our aim is to make people know about all precautions, and provide after disaster facility, rehabilitation, food supply, relief etc. </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

