                        <strong></strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr><p>
                    • Delivering services: provide adequate services related to requirement of human & environment<br>
• Training people: provide appropriate training to so that people will be able to face all those problems without any lacking.<br>
• Influencing people: influence people to adopt all those hygienic habits and acts to make their life safe and make the environment protected & clean.</p>
